OL,3,CYvette Cooper pledges crackdown on
OL,4,C'hateful beliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,7,Fpledged to crack down on people
OL,8,F"pushing harmful and hateful beliefs"
OL,9,Fand to "kickstart" a new approach to
OL,10,Ffighting extremism.
OL,12,FThe Home Office has commissioned a
OL,13,F"rapid sprint" to drive a new
OL,14,Fpractical approach to countering
OL,15,Fextremism.
OL,17,FThe project is being carried out to
OL,18,Fprovide analysis and recommendations
OL,19,Fon how to "tackle the threat posed by
OL,20,Fextremist ideologies".
