OL,6,FIt will inform a new Government
OL,7,Fcounter-extremism strategy to respond
OL,8,Fto growing and changing patterns
OL,9,Facross the UK.
OL,11,FThe Government said the scheme will
OL,12,Flook across the ideological spectrum,
OL,13,Fand address "gaps in the current
OL,14,Fsystem" which leave the country
OL,15,Fexposed to hateful activity that
OL,16,Fpromotes violence or undermines
OL,17,Fdemocracy.
