OL,4,C'hateful beliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FAfter the riots that broke out across
OL,7,FEngland following the stabbing of
OL,8,Fthree girls in Southport, a total of
OL,9,F460 people had appeared in
OL,10,Fmagistrates' courts relating to the
OL,11,Fdisorder by the end of Thursday.
OL,13,FAt least 72 people under the age of 18
OL,14,Fare believed to have been charged.
OL,16,FA number of people have also been
OL,17,Fhanded charges relating to publishing
OL,18,Fmaterial that contributed to rioting,
OL,19,Fsuch as publishing written material to
OL,20,Fstir up racial hatred or sending a
OL,21,Fgrossly offensive message.
