OL,3,CYvette Cooper pledges crackdown on
OL,4,C'hateful beliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FMs Cooper said: "For too long
OL,7,FGovernments have failed to address the
OL,8,Frise in extremism, both online and on
OL,9,Four streets, and we've seen the number
OL,10,Fof young people radicalised online
OL,11,Fgrow.
OL,13,F"Hateful incitement of all kinds
OL,14,Ffractures and frays the very fabric of
OL,15,Four communities and our democracy.
OL,17,F"Action against extremism has been
OL,18,Fbadly hollowed out in recent years,
OL,19,Fjust when it should have been needed
OL,20,Fmost.
