OL,3,CYvette Cooper pledges crackdown on
OL,4,C'hateful beliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,F"That work will underpin a new
OL,7,Fstrategic approach to countering
OL,8,Fextremism from Government, working
OL,9,Fclosely with communities to build
OL,10,Fconsensus and impetus for our plans".
OL,12,FThe Home Secretary had criticised the
OL,13,Fprevious government for having no
OL,14,Fcounter-extremism strategy since 2015,
OL,15,Fand that the lack of a comprehensive
OL,16,Fapproach or practical plans was
OL,17,Fleaving communities less safe.
