OL,3,CYvette Cooper pledges crackdown on
OL,4,C'hateful beliefs' to counter extremism
OL,6,FThe new strategy aims to deliver on
OL,7,Fthe Government's manifesto commitment
OL,8,Fof preventing people being drawn
OL,9,Ftowards hateful ideologies.
OL,11,FThe Home Office says it will look at
OL,12,Fthe rise of both Islamist and far-
OL,13,Fright extremism in the UK, as well as
OL,14,Fwider ideological trends, including
OL,15,Fextreme misogyny or beliefs that fit
OL,16,Finto broader categories like fixation
OL,17,Fon violence.
